474 private:
475 class AtomicCounterBindingState;
476 constexpr static size_t kAtomicCounterSize = 4;
477 // UNIFORM_ARRAY_STRIDE for atomic counter arrays is an implementation-dependent value which
478 // can be queried after a program is linked according to ES 3.10 section 7.7.1. This is
479 // controversial with the offset inheritance as described in ESSL 3.10 section 4.4.6. Currently
480 // we treat it as always 4 in favour of the original interpretation in
481 // "ARB_shader_atomic_counters".
482 // TODO(jie.a.chen@intel.com): Double check this once the spec vagueness is resolved.
483 // Note that there may be tests in AtomicCounter_test that will need to be updated as well.
484 constexpr static size_t kAtomicCounterArrayStride = 4;
